asset.hookText: Hi Candace. We saw your review on our site. Your WindTunnel 2 High Capacity should have strong suction, and the brushes shouldn't stop spinning. We have a few things to check. We put together a quick video to help. Let us know if you have any questions. We're always here to help! -Felicia
